cs in the presence of a\nstatic but inhomogeneous magnetic field can be derived. The Casimir invariants\nof the Poisson brackets of the derived fluid models are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Feb 2014 20:10:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Mar 2014 19:09:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
