s recently\nindicated by deep-focus time-distance helioseismology analysis of the SDO/HMI\nand SOHO/MDI data. We compare the new dynamo model with various characteristics\nif the solar magnetic cycles, including the cycle asymmetry (Waldmeier's\nrelations) and magnetic `butterfly' diagrams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2014 00:51:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-11"}
